                    class="block w-full bg-orange-500 hover:bg-orange-400 border border-orange-600 text-white text-center py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:glow-effect transition-all transform hover:scale-105"
                >
                    üì§ Compartir gato
                </button>

                <a 
